data.description: **Home has an assumable VA loan with an incredible 2.25% interest rate!**Welcome home to 1341 Hermitage Lane!  This stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home offers incredible features and a sophisticated design that is sure to impress.  Situated in a highly desired neighborhood, this house provides the perfect balance of comfort and style.As you enter the home, you will be greeted by a bright and spacious living room, adorned with large windows that allow ample natural light to flood the space.  The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining guests or enjoying family meals.The kitchen is a true chef's dream, featuring modern appliances, gorgeous countertops, and plenty of cabinet space for storage.Whether you are a culinary enthusiast or simply enjoy cooking for your loved ones, this kitchen and pantry will exceed your expectations.  The master bedroom (downstairs) offers a peaceful retreat, complete with a private ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet. The three additional bedrooms are upstairs; spacious and versatile, perfect for accommodating guests or creating a home office space.  Step outside into the backyard, and you will find a beautifully landscaped oasis, perfect for outdoor relaxation and entertaining. The patio area is ideal for hosting barbecues or simply enjoying a morning cup of coffee. The fenced-in yard offers privacy and security, providing a safe space for children and pets to play freely.  Located in the sought-after city of Ladson, this property brings you close to a wide range of amenities and conveniences. Explore the nearby shopping centers, restaurants, and entertainment options or take advantage of the parks and recreation areas that are just moments away.  The Hunters Bend neighborhood is highly desirable.  There is a gorgeous pool overlooking one many scenic ponds in the neighborhood.  There are walking/jogging trails and beautiful ponds throughout the neighborhood.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home! Contact us today to schedule a private showing of 1341 Hermitage Lane in Ladson, SC. This is your chance to experience a luxurious and comfortable lifestyle in a truly remarkable residence.
